[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">Spirit</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">upon</st> <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05752\" class=\"\">Oded</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"03318 06440\">met</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen to</st> me, <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st>! The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you when you <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">loyal to</st> him.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek</st> him, he will <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">respond</st> to you,<n id=\"3\" /> but <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> you <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">reject</st> him, he will <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">reject</st> you. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "For a <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">long</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> had <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> sought the one <st data-num=\"0571\" class=\"\">true</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> a <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> to <st data-num=\"03384\" class=\"\">instruct</st> them, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>. ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "Because of their <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">distress</st>, they <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turned back</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. They <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">sought</st> him, and he <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">responded</st> to them.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "In <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">those</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">days</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0369\">no</st> one could <st data-num=\"03318 0935\">travel</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">safely</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">total</st> <st data-num=\"04103\" class=\"\">chaos</st> had <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">overtaken</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">people</st> of the surrounding <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">lands</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "One <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> was <st data-num=\"03807\" class=\"\">crushed</st> by <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">another</st>, and one <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> by <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">another</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"02000\" class=\"\">caused</st> them to be in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">turmoil</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "But as for <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">be strong</st> and <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"07503 03027\">get discouraged</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> your <st data-num=\"06468\" class=\"\">work</st> will <st data-num=\"03426\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"07939\" class=\"\">rewarded</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> and the <st data-num=\"05016\" class=\"\">prophecy</st> of <st data-num=\"05752\" class=\"\">Oded</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st>, he was <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">encouraged</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> He <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">removed</st> the <st data-num=\"08251\" class=\"\">detestable idols</st> from the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st> and <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"05892 0834\">cities</st> he had <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">seized</st> in the <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraimite</st> <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hill country</st>. He <st data-num=\"02318\" class=\"\">repaired</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0834 06440\">in front of</st> the <st data-num=\"0197\" class=\"\">porch of the</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0197\" class=\"\">temple</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">He <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">assembled</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st>, as well as the <st data-num=\"01481\" class=\"\">settlers</st><n id=\"1\" /> from <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st>, <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>, and <st data-num=\"08095\" class=\"\">Simeon</st> who had come to live <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> them. <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">Many</st> people from <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> had <st data-num=\"03588 05307\">come</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">there</st> <st data-num=\"03588 05307\">to live</st><n id=\"2\" /> when they <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> his <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> was <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> him.",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">assembled</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> in the <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">third</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st> of the <st data-num=\"02568 06240\">fifteenth</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> of <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04438\" class=\"\">reign</st>. ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st><n id=\"1\" /> they <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrificed</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">some</st> of the <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st> they had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought back</st>, including <st data-num=\"07651 03967\">700</st> head of <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st> and <st data-num=\"07651 0505\">7,000</st> <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"0935 01285\">solemnly agreed</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st><n id=\"2\" /> with their <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">being</st>. ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">Anyone</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> would <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03608\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> would be <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">executed</st>, <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">whether</st> they were <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">young</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">old</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">male</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">female</st>. ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">swore</st> their <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">allegiance</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">shouting</st> their <st data-num=\"08643\" class=\"\">approval</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">loudly</st> and sounding <st data-num=\"02689\" class=\"\">trumpets</st> and <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">horns</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> <st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">was happy</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> the <st data-num=\"07621\" class=\"\">oath</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">made</st> the <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">vow</st> with their <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st>. They <st data-num=\"03605 07522\">willingly</st> <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">sought</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> and he <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">responded</st> to them.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">He</st> <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">made</st> them <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">secure</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">on every side</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">removed</st> <st data-num=\"04601\" class=\"\">Maacah</st> his <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">grandmother</st><n id=\"1\" /> from her position as <st data-num=\"01377\" class=\"\">queen mother</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">because</st> she had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">made</st> a <st data-num=\"04656\" class=\"\">loathsome</st> <st data-num=\"0842\" class=\"\">Asherah pole</st>. <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">cut down</st> her <st data-num=\"04656\" class=\"\">loathsome pole</st> and <st data-num=\"01854\" class=\"\">crushed</st> and <st data-num=\"08313\" class=\"\">burned</st> it in the <st data-num=\"06939\" class=\"\">Kidron</st> <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">Valley</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"01116\" class=\"\">high places</st> were <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">eliminated</st> from <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"07535\" class=\"\">yet</st> <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">wholeheartedly</st> <st data-num=\"08003\" class=\"\">devoted</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">throughout</st> his <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">lifetime</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> the <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">holy items</st> that his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st> <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">and</st> he had made into <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>, including the <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>, <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, and other <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">articles</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">There <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> more <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> the <st data-num=\"07970\" class=\"\">thirty</st>-<st data-num=\"02568\" class=\"\">fifth</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> of <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04438\" class=\"\">reign</st>. ",
    "verse": "19"
  }
]